Who Do You Think You Are? Australia - Series 7, Episode 5




Dawn Fraser

Australian sporting icon Dawn Fraser is on the trail of the grandparents she never knew. Her search takes her back to her childhood home, in Balmain, Sydney. Next, Dawn's investigation takes her to the birth place of her grandfather - Peru.




Original Air Date: 01-Sep-2015
